Text: I swore my life to Legatus Noah! Behold the depth of my loyalty!
We cannot win this battle! Tsubame!
Remember this defeat well, shinobi. As brothers and sisters of Doma, we showed mercy this time. We will not do so again.
You are...much changed. What have those fiends done to you!?
Witness the strength of the IVth Legion!
Victory and glory are ours! Inform command!
I am Pagaga of House Vochstein, queen of all beastkind! Cower before me!
“The Vochsteins are renowned in the West for their beast-taming prowess,” you say? You know this girl?
Ahahaha! Father's exploits are sung of far and wide! Should you wish to flee, now is your chance!
The girl has skill befitting one of Lyon's students, I'll give her that.
“The Vochsteins have long been Lyon's rivals for the title of Beast King,” you say? I say, old friend, where do you learn these things?
Rivals, you say!? Hah! That weanling Lyon is not fit to wear Father's skivvies!
You sully the name of House Vochstein...and you shall pay for this dishonor with your lives!
No... What have you done to my beauties!?
Pagaga will remember this day. The next time we meet, my beauties will drink of your blood!
Lyon has quite the reputation, but it seems he's not the only one with these skills...
Indeed. We had best return, restock, and report our findings.
Curses! These damn beasts are too strong for us! Fall back! We'll take our chances another day!
Gahaha! This is the strength of House Vochstein, rulers of all beastkind!
Who needs that greybeard Lyon!? Pagaga and her beauties will smite the Resistance single-handedly!

Hull integrity at 60%. Firepower insufficient.
Requesting helldiver reinforcements.

Sir, we have movement.
Magitek armor inbound!
We must be ready for every eventuality!
We must have faith in Arenvald and Fordola!
The seat of the Amalj'aa's power doth lie beyond this valley...
We must be ready for every eventuality!
We must have faith in Arenvald and Fordola!
The kobolds have proven to be staunch allies indeed!
The kobolds have proven to be staunch allies indeed!
I think this answers the question of how they summoned Bahamut...
It's fast, but not fast enough!
I think this answers the question of how they summoned Bahamut...
In death, may you find the peace you were denied in life...
The Amalj'aa need all the help they can get. Come on!
In death, may you find the peace you were denied in life...
We must proceed with caution if we wish to slip through the enemy's front line.
With Estinien and Tiamat on our side, we have nothing to fear!
Estinien! Leave these foes to us!
Let us follow Tiamat and Ser Estinien's lead!
Estinien! Leave these foes to us!
One could not ask for more dependable allies!
The armies of the Alliance have entered the fray.
Let's lend the Ishgardians our support!
Our presence is yet required in the city.
The armies of the Alliance have entered the fray.

There is no time to lose.
To the valley!
Together, we will force the enemy back!
It seems Estinien is good for something after all.
It seems Estinien is good for something after all.

As you should well know!
Or have you been ignoring my tales of his exploits?
Another of the Empire's magitek monstrosities, it would seem.
That unsightly contraption is in need of dismantling.

Absurdly large and ugly as sin?
There's no mistaking that “classic” Garlean design...

A mobile fortress...
So, 'tis more than a mere rumor.

A mobile fortress...
So, 'tis more than a mere rumor.
The Telophoroi are not leaving anything to chance...
My goodness... I do hope there aren't any more of those!

The Amalj'aa could teach
me a thing or two about pyromancy.
I dread to think how we'd have fared without the Amalj'aa!
The enemy's assault on the city hath been thwarted.
The enemy's assault on the city hath been thwarted.
I never dreamed I would have the chance to ride a dragon!
Surely, teleportation magick presenteth a safer alternative...
Surely, teleportation magick presenteth a safer alternative...

It's perfectly safe!
At least, I think it is...
We all made it here in one piece, I take it?
Twelve forfend I should make such a perilous journey again...
Twelve forfend I should make such a perilous journey again...
If you thought that was nerve-racking, the worst is yet to come...

The air is thick with aether...
We are close.
This is not Bahamut, just a poor imitation!
This is not Bahamut, just a poor imitation!
Imitation or no, we would be fools to underestimate it!

Isn't he precious!?
I brushed his coat just for the occasion!
Time for your daily exercise, my pet.
Did I not hire you to provide enrichment for my newest acquisition?
He does so love to stomp, you see. There's nothing he enjoys more than the sound of shattering bone...

Save your grisly threats─our courage will not be so easily shaken.
Form up! We take this oversized beast down!

You've had your fun, Lyuba!
No more playing now!
Why...? Why am I here...down in the dirt?
I will see you all ground into meat slop!
Your minced remains will fill the feeding troughs of my menagerie!

Do not give chase! You only risk being ambushed.
See to the wounded, and keep watch for approaching enemies.

I must say, this Clarricie is proving to be a problem.
Where does she keep finding all these fantastic beasts?

A mystery for another day, perhaps.
Come, let us make our way back to camp...

You useless, spineless worms.
Lyuba must have more exercise than that!

We cannot risk any more casualties.
Gather the wounded and quit the field!
Test subjects confirmed dead. Commencing aether extraction...
Resistance fighters? What's going on here!?

He's calling in fire support, but this is no time to withdraw!
We stand our ground!
Let's take a moment to assess the situation.

Everyone ready?
Then let's not dally any longer!
Not your average dragon, by the looks of it...
So much for the Telophoroi's fancy new toy.
So much for the Telophoroi's fancy new toy.
This will save us a long trek.
Unnngh...my head... I have to get home... My family, they need me...
Unnngh... Wh-Who are you? Stay away! Stay away from me!
Be calm, my friend. We are here to help you.
\\<bzzzt> Excellent, they have taken the bait. Commence armament test.
What was that voice? An enemy transmission!?

This...this is hyperpilot Dabog.
Order acknowledged. Deploying long-range assault nodes.
Keep calm! We came here to save Dabog, and we will stay the course!
Please, Dabog! Come to your senses! We are not your enemy!

This is hyperpilot Dabog. Energy levels below minimum.
Combat capabilities severely compromised. Returning to base.
Yet again we have failed our friend, and he remains at the enemy's mercy...
There is nothing left to be done here. Let us return to the encampment.

No... Defeat is an insult to my queen!
I will hold back nothing. NOTHING!
The Onmyoji Brotherhood answers to none but Lord Noah! We will see his dream realized!
Master Oboro, we cannot follow. We must rally more troops.
You're right, of course. Let's return home.
Now this is a fine collection of eggs!
Pray assist us again if you've time to spare during the festival!

These “roosters” are demons in feathered form!
I fear we've no choice but to abandon our efforts...
It's too late...too late for us all...
We must share the brunt of the blow!

This is where our ways do part.
We shall survey the halls below.

Scanning for targets...
Scanning for targets...

You're one of us, right?
We need your help!
We'll make it out of this─together!
We have to get back to the shelter!
That wall─our attacks cannot penetrate it!
Not to worry─unlike you, I'm not a baby.
It's about bloody time, ye bastards!
Gahaha! I'm starting to enjoy this!
Your lot brought the pestilence! You!
Purify them with fire, I say!
How did it come to this?
It means to kill us all!
If I can reach the terminal...
I did it! I killed them all!
Finally, I'm free! I...I think. I hope...
Is this the end for usss?
What in blazes is wrong with these doors!?
I'm never getting out of here, am I?
You've led us in circles again, you fat-tailed idiot!
Oh yeah? Well...your mother smells like cabbage!
Keep calm and watch your step!
Ha! They'll have to do better than that!
Let's put on a good show, eh?
The carriages are in safe hands!
To victory─come hells or high water!
The Duke of Destruction has descended!
I've been itchin' for a good scrap!
All must bow before the Sun!
Think you can kill me!?I would like to see you try!
We will grow strong through conquest!
There is no future without our star!
Those not with us are against us!
Unidentified presence detected... Eliminate unknown life-forms!
Failure is not an acceptable pathway. Commencing annihilation.
Nothing can halt our forward march!
Crush the enemy! Turn them to scrap!
War with other stars ensures advancement!
We must revitalize our star to secure stability!
Eukrasian Diagnosis, if you'd be so kind!
Fiends ahead! Please watch my back!
Oh, how I have waited for this moment.
Oh no! It thinks we're the intruders!
I say we get out of here!
The security system is out of control!
Your pitiful threat does not compute!
Why, you worthless piece of scrap...!
You're a scourge upon our star!
My friends! We fight as one!
The weave of a shinobi's power!
